author: Tracey Peterson
title: Tracey Peterson
text: I accidentally purchased the wrong atomizer bodies, because they were the smaller ones I had no empty cartridges that fit. I spoke with Natalie and explained my dilemma. She double checked to ensure that the larger atomizer was no longer in stock and sent me 10 empty cartridges for the atomizers I had purchased so I would be able to use them. Natalie was terrific.
